about.summary: Python wrapper for MurmurHash (MurmurHash3), a set of fast and robust hash functions.

name: mmh3
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "mmh3" %}
{% set version = "2.5.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/hajimes/{{ name|lower }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2fe4ee15ca09ea48a7bb6493f2a6d2e7659f33af4d46e6b39ff35d77b549e80f

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv"

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}

  host:
    - python
    - pip

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - mmh3

about:
  home: http://packages.python.org/mmh3
  license: CC0-1.0
  license_family: CC
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Python wrapper for MurmurHash (MurmurHash3), a set of fast and robust hash functions.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - johnlees
